      <description>
        
          &lt;h2 id=&#34;1-introduction&#34;&gt;1. Introduction&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the real world, we can identify the difference between String and Number in a simple way as below mention.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-fallback&#34; data-lang=&#34;fallback&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;  113 is Number
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;  29.9 is Number
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;  9.9d is Number
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;  xyz is Not a Number
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;  -369 is Number
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the above example, you see that &amp;quot;XYZ&amp;quot; is String as we clearly identify manually But it is difficult to identify using some code.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-question-to-be-asked&#34;&gt;2. Question to be asked&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is more than one way anyone can ask this question as below:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;check-if-the-string-is-int&#34;&gt;Check if the string is int&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;in-java-check-if-the-string-is-a-number&#34;&gt;In JAVA check if the string is a number&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;check-if-the-string-is-number-java&#34;&gt;Check if the string is number java&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;in-java-check-if-the-string-is-numeric&#34;&gt;In JAVA check if the string is numeric&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;how-can-identify-input-is-a-string-or-integer-in-jav&#34;&gt;How can identify input is a string or integer in jav&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;a?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-practical-code&#34;&gt;2. Practical Code&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is mainly two way we can give above all answer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;211-logical-code-using-java&#34;&gt;2.1.1 Logical Code Using JAVA:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;kd&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kd&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nc&#34;&gt;NumberCheck&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 2&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 3&lt;/span&gt;	&lt;span class=&#34;kd&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kd&#34;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nf&#34;&gt;main&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;[]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;args&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 4&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 5&lt;/span&gt;		&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;113 is numeric : &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;isNumericCheck&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;113&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 6&lt;/span&gt;		&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;29.9 is numeric : &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;isNumericCheck&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;29.9&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 7&lt;/span&gt;		&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;9.9d is numeric : &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;isNumericCheck&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;9.9d&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 8&lt;/span&gt;		&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;xyz is numeric : &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;isNumericCheck&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;xyz&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 9&lt;/span&gt;		&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;-369 is numeric : &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;isNumericCheck&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;-369&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;	&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;13&lt;/span&gt;	&lt;span class=&#34;kd&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kd&#34;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;boolean&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nf&#34;&gt;isNumericCheck&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;str&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;14&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;15&lt;/span&gt;		&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;str&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kc&#34;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;||&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;str&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;length&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;16&lt;/span&gt;			&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kc&#34;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;17&lt;/span&gt;		&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;18&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;19&lt;/span&gt;		&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;			&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;Double&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;parseDouble&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;str&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;21&lt;/span&gt;			&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kc&#34;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;22&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;23&lt;/span&gt;		&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;NumberFormatException&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;e&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;24&lt;/span&gt;			&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kc&#34;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;25&lt;/span&gt;		&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;26&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;27&lt;/span&gt;	&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;28&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;29&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;30&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;output&#34;&gt;Output&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-fallback&#34; data-lang=&#34;fallback&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;  113 is numeric : true
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;  29.9 is numeric : true
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;  9.9d is numeric : true
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;  xyz is numeric : false
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;  -369 is numeric : true
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h4 id=&#34;212-using-depedency-or-library-in-java-project&#34;&gt;2.1.2 Using Depedency or Library in JAVA project.&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You need to add below depedency in your project.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-fallback&#34; data-lang=&#34;fallback&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;   &amp;lt;dependency&amp;gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;    &amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;org.apache.commons&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;    &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;commons-lang3&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;    &amp;lt;version&amp;gt;3.11&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;  &amp;lt;/dependency&amp;gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 1&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;kn&#34;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nn&#34;&gt;org.apache.commons.lang3.math.NumberUtils&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 2&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;kd&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kd&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nc&#34;&gt;NumberCheck&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 3&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 4&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;kd&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kd&#34;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nf&#34;&gt;main&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;[]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;args&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 5&lt;/span&gt;      
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 6&lt;/span&gt;      
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 7&lt;/span&gt;      
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 8&lt;/span&gt;              &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;113 is numeric : &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;NumberUtils&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;isCreatable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;113&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt; 9&lt;/span&gt;              &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;29.9 is numeric : &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;NumberUtils&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;isCreatable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;29.9&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;              &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;9.9d is numeric : &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;NumberUtils&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;isCreatable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;9.9d&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;              &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;xyz is numeric : &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;NumberUtils&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;isCreatable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;xyz&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;              &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;System&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;-369 is numeric : &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;NumberUtils&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;isCreatable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;-369&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;13&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;14&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;15&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;16&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;output-1&#34;&gt;Output&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-fallback&#34; data-lang=&#34;fallback&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;  113 is numeric : true
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;  29.9 is numeric : true
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;  9.9d is numeric : true
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;  xyz is numeric : false
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;  -369 is numeric : true
&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;3-conclusion&#34;&gt;3. Conclusion&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To put it in nutshell in this article we got brief knowledge about identifying a String is a number or not. We identify both ways via external library and codebase.&lt;/p&gt;

        
